        <mxCell id="1J0Z1twBoM3idAmu7u2K-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Requirements&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;User should be able the see calendar in multiple views like Weekly, Monthly, Yearly&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;User should be able to see the events created for a day in Weekly, Monthly view arranged by start time&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;User should be able to create new events, delete/modify old events&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;User should be able to select start/end date/time and should be able to invite other user in a event&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
